fragment_downloaded_cb({"url":"design/2008_design/2008_UI_Design.html#image-property-editor","fragment":"Image Property Editor\nThe user can add still images to the timeline. By default the image is\nletterboxed to the current project resolution, but these defaults can be\nchanged to suit the users's needs.\n First the user selects the image in the\ntimeline\n The image property editor appears in the\nproperty browser.\n The user can crop the image to an arbitrary\nregion.\n\n The user can scale the image as appropriate.\n The user can also set the orientation of the\nimage.\n"});